      "height": 219,
      "content": "Design a mission control chat interface into “stratos-Pre-Flight” frame for an AI-assisted high-altitude balloon operations platform with a sidebar, showing history and pinned chats. Add a header bar showing navigation for Chat, Pre-Flight, Mission Control, and Post-Flight, and a central content area with a conversational AI chat, including message history, structured mission data (trajectory, weather, NOTAMs), and an input bar, with an optional right panel displaying a live map with trajectory overlays and launch/landing markers, using a dark, aerospace mission control style."
